(12253, 'Vetoyagra 100 mg 12 oro-dispersible tabs.', 'فيتوياجرا 100 مجم 12 قرص ذائب بالفم', '66', '96', 'Sildenafil', 'Rameda', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '100 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
